<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gürr & Duru Hukuk Bürosu</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .hero-overlay {
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero-content {
            pointer-events: auto;
        }
        .navbar-spacing {
            height: 2rem !important; /* 32px */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <div class="relative">
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="relative bg-gray-900 min-h-[500px] md:h-[600px] hero-section pt-16" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg'); background-position: center; background-size: cover;">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-50"></div>
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 flex items-center h-full">
                <div class="text-white w-full md:w-2/3">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Hukuki Çözüm Ortağınız</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8">Gürr & Duru Hukuk Bürosu olarak, 20 yıllık tecrübemizle hukuki ihtiyaçlarınıza profesyonel çözümler sunuyoruz.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
                        <a href="/iletisim" class="bg-white text-gray-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300 text-center">
                            Ücretsiz Danışmanlık
                        </a>
                        <a href="/hizmetlerimiz" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition duration-300 text-center">
                            Hizmetlerimiz
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hizmetler Section -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Hizmetlerimiz</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
            Uzman kadromuz ile ticaret hukuku, aile hukuku ve ceza hukuku başta olmak üzere geniş bir yelpazede hukuki danışmanlık ve avukatlık hizmetleri sunuyoruz.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Ticaret Hukuku</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Şirketler hukuku, ticari sözleşmeler ve uyuşmazlık çözümü konularında profesyonel hizmet.</p>
                <a href="/hizmetlerimiz/ticaret-hukuku" class="text-gray-900 font-semibold hover:text-gray-600 transition duration-300">Detaylı Bilgi →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Aile Hukuku</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Boşanma, velayet, nafaka ve miras hukuku alanlarında uzman danışmanlık.</p>
                <a href="/hizmetlerimiz/aile-hukuku" class="text-gray-900 font-semibold hover:text-gray-600 transition duration-300">Detaylı Bilgi →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Ceza Hukuku</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Ceza davalarında savunma ve hukuki danışmanlık hizmetleri.</p>
                <a href="/hizmetlerimiz/ceza-hukuku" class="text-gray-900 font-semibold hover:text-gray-600 transition duration-300">Detaylı Bilgi →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Neden Biz Section -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Neden Gürr & Duru?</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
                20 yıllık tecrübemiz ve uzman kadromuzla, müvekkillerimize en iyi hukuki hizmeti sunuyoruz.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Güvenilirlik</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">20 yıllık tecrübe ve profesyonel yaklaşım</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Hızlı Çözüm</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Süreçlerin hızlı ve etkili yönetimi</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">İletişim</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Sürekli bilgilendirme ve şeffaf iletişim</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Uzmanlık</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Alanında uzman avukat kadrosu</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 